      "message": "\u003e \u003e Yep, I just double checked it.\n\u003e \u003e I tested with NDK r14, x86_64.\n\u003e \n\u003e Maybe it was only fixed recently. Guess we can’t rely on that. Thanks for checking.\n\nDunno what’s up, but since I was doing NDK work anyway, I just tried with NDK r14 and readelf -l still shows, for crashpad_util_test targeting x86_64:\n\n  NOTE           0x0000000000000216 0x0000000000000216 0x0000000000000216\n                 0x0000000000000098 0x0000000000000098  R      0x2\n\n(p_align is the last field)",
